            "title": "普陀山4消防重裝備代客焚香過香火  網民：打不過就加入︱有片",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/a3d9a20fabcb1d8233b60650c1934ebb/2025-02/New_Project_84485956526.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/10985f06e2b971ef9b9b87c7361c0102/058f946146a34f89a89529f6a4389cbc-9eb09cb6f18ca88a74c701209ae0301b-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67a2a533d15ce\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67a2a533d15d0\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"普陀山安排消防員代善信焚香過香火，獲網民大讚。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/232a2829ea690521ada5cfea791f0b63/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250204/_2025020419062295197.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">普陀山安排消防員代善信焚香過香火，獲網民大讚。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>中國四大佛教名山之一的浙江普陀山，在農曆新年期間例必出現「人从众」場面，今年最吸晴的是有穿上專業消防服、眼罩、耐熱手套的消防員，為數以萬計善男信女焚香、熏物過香火。網民大讚他們手法嫻熟專業，亦有人笑指消防員阻不了遊客燃點香燭，只好「打不過便加入」。\n\n</p><h2>防火服、眼罩、手套齊備</h2>\n<p>據九派新聞報道，數以萬計的遊客在農曆新年期間到訪普陀山。為保障群眾及寺廟安全，4名消防員幫助香客焚香。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4058530/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"普陀山安排消防員替善信焚香、過香火，獲網民大讚。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/66329cda508ae711c5477ae2dc0a7a3a/2025-02/5445_1_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        普陀山安排消防員替善信焚香、過香火，獲網民大讚。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4058531/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"普陀山安排消防員替善信焚香、過香火，獲網民大讚。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fb5143532acc7f6a6aa8b2c5b53cbaaf/2025-02/5445_2_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        普陀山安排消防員替善信焚香、過香火，獲網民大讚。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4058532/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"普陀山是中國4大佛教名山，每到農曆新年均有萬計善信湧來上香。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/870476eee4936f51279d36072d6a3b68/2025-02/5445_3_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        普陀山是中國4大佛教名山，每到農曆新年均有萬計善信湧來上香。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4058533/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"普陀山是中國4大佛教名山，每到農曆新年均有萬計善信湧來上香。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.h