            "title": "天文台｜今早相當清涼 市區氣溫降至13、14度 新界再低幾度",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/6dc7ec30fdfd960595afb5657d368521/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250205/_2025020507092136301.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>一股偏東氣流正影響廣東沿岸。同時，廣東天色大致良好。本港今早相當清涼，市區氣溫降至13、14度，新界再低幾度。\n\n</p>\n<p>本港地區今日天氣預測，初時大致天晴。日間乾燥，最高氣溫約19度。稍後漸轉多雲。吹和緩至清勁東至東北風。\n\n</p>\n<p>展望未來一兩日大致多雲，早上持續清涼。星期五漸轉吹偏北風，週末期間早上寒冷，市區最低氣溫在11度左右，新界再低幾度。下週初天色好轉，日間非常乾燥。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060099/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"分區氣溫\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/875f9810eb0adfe7c0f8afc50aed9ac2/2025-02/2025-02-05_07_06_07.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        分區氣溫\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060100/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"九天天氣預報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dffa71deef51d39c445e9e70512638f1/2025-02/2025-02-05_07_06_55.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        九天天氣預報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060101/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"今早相當清涼。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0b8ca59a9c904b70a0fb7189aa668942/2025-02/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-02-05-07-02-40_001.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        今早相當清涼。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060102/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"市區氣溫降至13、14度。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/385525b5961346d0da4b19911c239ff4/2025-02/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-02-05-07-02-43_003.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        市區氣溫降至13、14度。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4060103/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"新界再低幾度。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f4073b3ca959804010bb1b38dc45f66a/2025-02/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-02-05-07-02-40_002.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        新界再低幾度。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>受一股清勁至強風程度的偏東氣流影響，未來一兩日廣東沿岸雲量逐漸增多，有一兩陣微雨，早上持續清涼。預料一股強烈冬季季候風會在接近週末抵達華南沿岸，週末期間該區早上寒冷，內陸地區嚴寒。下週初華南天色好轉，日間非常乾燥。隨著季候風被偏東氣流取代，下週中期廣東沿岸氣溫回升。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
